title: FC Energiya Chaykovsky
text: FC Energiya Chaykovsky () is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> team from <a href="Chaykovsky%2C%20Perm%20Krai">Chaykovsky</a>. It played professionally from 1992 to 2002. Its best result was fourth place in the <a href="Russian%20Second%20Division">Russian Second Division</a> (Zone Center in 1997 and Zone Ural in 1998). Since 2009, it plays in the lower level amateur league.
